<p><persName>Mr Stephen F. Austin</persName> In acct With <persName>J Pettit</persName></p>

<p><date n="xx-xx-1813">1813</date></p>

<p><date when="1813-12-25">Decr. 25</date> To 1 Bottle Essence peppermint______________      50

<date n="xx-xx-1814">1814 </date>To your part of why. and Sugar__________________      37 1/2

<date when="1814-01-23">Jany 23</date> To Merehz pd Boy pr order____________________   2. 75

To 1 Deck cards______________________________________      75
									  ________
Amount due me________________________________________   4. 37 1/2</p>

<p><date when="1814-02-06">Feby 6th 1814</date></p>
<p>Recd Payt infull</p>

<p><persName>J Pettit</persName></p>

